headline.main: Soccer: London Mayor Approves Chelsea's New 'Jewel' of a Stadium
headline.print_headline: Soccer: London Mayor Approves Chelsea's New 'Jewel' of a Stadium

lead_paragraph: Chelsea's plans for a new 60,000-capacity stadium at their historic Stamford Bridge home have been approved by Mayor of London Sadiq Khan.
